00:03:37.256 --> 00:03:38.876 A:middle
If people understood this and it

00:03:38.876 --> 00:03:41.076 A:middle
scared them, why should we be

00:03:41.076 --> 00:03:41.916 A:middle
doing it at all?

00:03:43.116 --> 00:03:45.226 A:middle
Could we use less granular data,

00:03:45.226 --> 00:03:46.476 A:middle
less precise?

00:03:47.416 --> 00:03:48.656 A:middle
Are there other approaches we

00:03:48.656 --> 00:03:49.466 A:middle
should consider?

00:03:50.616 --> 00:03:52.316 A:middle
