00:10:21.186 --> 00:10:21.626 A:middle
your name.

00:10:21.626 --> 00:10:22.646 A:middle
They know whose data it is.

00:10:23.676 --> 00:10:24.906 A:middle
So you can't just make this data

00:10:24.906 --> 00:10:25.846 A:middle
