00:10:56.666 --> 00:10:58.006 A:middle
sensitive information, we still

00:10:58.006 --> 00:10:59.416 A:middle
provide control through things

00:10:59.416 --> 00:11:00.896 A:middle
like being able to reset that


00:10:59.416 --> 00:11:00.896 A:middle
like being able to reset that

