from your area.

00:16:37.636 --> 00:16:39.396 A:middle
Remember, if users understand

00:16:39.396 --> 00:16:41.136 A:middle
why they're being asked for this

00:16:41.136 --> 00:16:42.206 A:middle
data, they're going to be more

00:16:42.206 --> 00:16:44.596 A:middle
likely to allow it.

00:16:44.726 --> 00:16:45.946 A:middle
If you were building a transit

00:16:45.946 --> 00:16:47.296 A:middle
app for a subway system, you

00:16:47.596 --> 00:16:48.876 A:middle
might write something like this.

